name: RISE Worship CD
description:
Live worship from Roanoke by The Jonathan Project (Inlightened Ministries). 

The Jonathan Project is:
Craig Tackett - vocals
Brittany Tackett - vocals
Kevin Robison - guitars, vocals
Daniel Griffith - guitars
Brandon Wilson - piano, keyboard, vocals
Thomas Frankie - bass
Will Fryar - drums

Tracks:
1. spring of life
2. sing sing sing
3. rise and sing  
4. taste and see
5. beautiful jesus
6. i surrender all  
7. revelation song
8. extraordinary love
9. hosanna  
10. wrap me in your arms
11. bless the lord  
12. glory to god
13. let god arise
